name: Elemental Portal: Earth
description: Piece created using sacred geometry and symbols with the intention of connecting directly with the deep all-knowing parts of your soul. This piece connects with the element of Earth, bringing stability, structure, abundance, and fertility. Earth is the element which nurtures all of the rest, providing solid ground from which life can blossom. It rules the physical body, connecting us with the pleasures of the material experience as a means for spiritual developement.
